0.26.0

Display full images on solo page.
Remove side margins on mobile.
Significant refactor of websocket system.
Refactor CSRF system.
Refactor template variables.
Reorganization of JS code.

0.25.0

Improved rejection and ban handling.
More conventional custom scrollbar.
Prevent re-downloading of Youtube thumbnails.

0.24.0

Allow user to decide account cookie duration.
Add ability to log out all devices.
Combine "anon" and "csrf" cookies into "session" cookie.

0.23.0

Download Youtube thumbnails locally.

0.22.0

Add CSRF prevention tokens.

0.21.0

Use alphanumeric keys.
Optimize Youtube display.

0.20.0

Use webp thumbnails, including for animated images.

0.19.0

Use pgcrypto for passwords instead of Argon2 library.
Add the ability for a user to change his password.

0.18.0

Use GnuPG for upload encryption instead of Cocoon.

0.17.0

Allow setting a preferred time zone.

0.16.0

Generate optimized thumbnails for most image types.

0.15.0

Add flexbox index display and more detailed solo display.

0.14.2

Allow 700px max width of media.

0.14.1

Clean up messaging when a post is banned.
Fix interim fetching when a displayed post has been banned.
Display alert message if fetch fails.

0.14.0

Add more aesthetic routes.

0.13.0

Allow modding after post approval.

0.12.0

Fetch interim posts upon websocket connect.

0.11.0

Add YouTube Shorts support.

0.10.1

Remove columns and add a 1200px maximum width.

0.10.0

Add JavaScript fetch support to post and review forms.
Attempt reconnection to websocket.
Use multi-column display on wider browsers.

0.9.1

Increase maximum media height to 2000px.

0.9.0

Add manual banning with full post deletion.

0.8.3

Add lazy loading of images and iframes.
Allow for wide browser sizes if desired.
Increase per-page limit to 1,000.

0.8.2

Fix bug where YouTube iframes were not preserving 16:9 aspect ratio at short widths.
Also expand width of iframes to fill their container at larger sizes.

0.8.1

Fix a bug where iframe embeds were too wide in small browsers (like mobile).

0.8.0

Add YouTube iframe embeds.

0.7.0

Add simple pagination system for accessing a next page after the limit is reached.

0.6.1

Fixed a bug where providing a non-existent "from" post caused an error.

0.6.0

Added the ability to list posts from a starting post.
The title text and post author text are now links.

0.5.0

Auto-link all posted URLs. Retroactively link URLs in old posts.

0.4.0

Add support for video and audio files.
The pub/images directory has been renamed to pub/media.

0.3.2

Delete encrypted cocoon file upon image approval as well as rejection.

0.3.1

Add rsync of production images to reload script.

0.3.0

Add support for image uploads. The images are encrypted upon upload. Only the
admin(s) can view them.
